casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-226. Prudential Property & Cas. Ins. Co. v. LaMarr.

Lorain County, No. 93CA005571. This cause is pending before the court on the filing of a motion for an order directing the Court of Appeals for Lorain County to certify its record. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective April 20, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
